This code is for the ad serving control of the game on Facebook.
(1) The code is divided into two categories, from the name tag to
see if it has an op prefix;
(2) The high-frequency control for the adset without the operation
prefix is ​​to provide the DAILY_BUDGET and _amount modification
control according to the feedback quickly, and the control strength
cannot trigger the re-learning of the advertisement. The ultimate goal
is to divide the daset into a stable delivery state through a strategy,
request a reorganization target that is not performing well, and then
enter the system again;
(3) With the operation prefix to enter the stable delivery, here is
just some strategies to control dailiy_budget.